d jedem Lexikontext Literaturhinweise beigegeben. Das Werk ist zudem mit einem Personen-, Orts- und Sachregister ausgestattet.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 08. Jun 2020) 7aHISTORY / Modern / 20th Century.2bisacsh1 aBrandes, Detlef, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKaiserová, Kristina, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMyeshkov, Dmytro, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aRuchniewicz, Krzysztof, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aSundhaussen, Holm, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aTroebst, Stefan, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBöhlau Complete Package 2010-2013z978311048981140uhttps://doi.org/10.7767/boehlau.9783205790075423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783205790075.jpg  a978-3-11-048981-1  Böhlau Complete Package 2010-2013c2010d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles